<p>
<seg id="1">I will do my best for Turkey</seg>
<seg id="2">The Olympic second runner up is Turkey’s record holder.</seg>
<seg id="3">He was born in Cuba, but he came to consider Turkey his homeland, when he came for Fenerbahçe...</seg>
<seg id="4">He became a Turkish citizen in 2013 and donned the national uniform...</seg>
<seg id="5">First, he became European champion, and then Olympic second runner up...</seg>
<seg id="6">And now, he’s one of Turkey’s most important medal hopes in the World Athletics Championship.</seg>
