<seg id="1">Don’t lose you teeth while trying to whiten them.</seg>
<seg id="2">Snow white teeth and an aesthetic smile are everyone’s dream.</seg>
<seg id="3">While people are trying everything to whiten their teeth, Nükhet Berk, the Chairperson of the Oral Laser Applications Association, warned people to keep away from products sold in markets or over the internet.</seg>
<seg id="4">Stressing that those products being sold are scratching the teeth’s dentin surfaces and colouring the teeth irreversibly, Nukhet Berk said "Whitening of the teeth can be attained by the chemical materials applied by dentists or by porcelain surfaces stuck onto the teeth’s surfaces like a nail".</seg>
<seg id="5">Explaining that preservative dental health prevents several diseases while implementing aesthetic applications and supplying a nice appearance for the teeth, the gums are important for mental health, Mr Berk said:</seg>
<seg id="6">Unless there is a structural problem or some genetic factor, the teeth of the youth are generally white.</seg>
<seg id="7">Because of aging, smoking, scratches in the dentin, or the drinking of caustic or dark colored drinks, the teeth tend to become darker over the years.</seg>
<seg id="8">Whitening of the teeth can be attained by the chemical materials applied by dentists or by porcelain surfaces stuck onto the teeth’s surfaces in the same way as nail extensions.</seg>
<seg id="9">Never use products sold in markets or over the internet to whiten teeth.</seg>
<seg id="10">That is because these materials scratch the dentin surface, so that teeth are irreversibly colored.</seg>
