<seg id="24">Saying that "traitors on a leash will go mad and burn to ashes in the fire of factionalism", the MHP’s Buyukataman grouped all the opposition parties and terror groups together, claiming that "From the CHP to the HDP to the Perincek group, from the PKK to FETO, whoever does whatever deed, the Turkish nation’s determination to define its own destiny will never be plotted against."</seg>
