<seg id="9">According to this account, Gloria Trevisan talked to her mother a couple of times during the two hours after the fire broke out at 01:00 local time.</seg>
<seg id="10">Initially speaking more calmly, Trevisan had said "Mom, something bad is happening here, fire has broken out."</seg>
<seg id="11">We are stranded, we can’t go out.</seg>
