<p>
<seg id="1">Soldier’s pump-action shotgun turns sendoff into terror: Five-year old Yildizsu could lose her eyesight</seg>
<seg id="2">Blood was shed during a soldiers’ sendoff in Eyup.</seg>
<seg id="3">The night before, a crowd had gathered at a park in the Karadolap neighborhood to send off their newly enlisted friends.</seg>
<seg id="4">According to allegations, M.K. and O.A. from the group had from time to time shot in the air with pump-action shotguns.</seg>
<seg id="5">The group started dispersing after the sending-off ceremony.</seg>
<seg id="6">M.K. fired a single shot into the ground with pump-action shotgun while passing by a playground full of children.</seg>
<seg id="7">Five people, including one child were sitting on a bank in the park and were injured as the buckshot ricocheted off the ground.</seg>
<seg id="8">These seconds were captured by the park’s security cameras.</seg>
<seg id="9">Ferhat Turan, Ercan Turan, Kader Balkir, Yildizsu Unus and Inci Kaya were injured and taken to nearby hospitals by ambulance.</seg>
<seg id="10">It was reported that among the injured undergoing treatment, five-year old Yildizsu Unus faces the risk of losing her left eye.</seg>
<seg id="11">Yildizsu’s grandmother, Meryem Kaya, described those moments to DHA.</seg>
<seg id="12">She said that the incident took place while her granddaughter was on her lap, "The soldiers’ sendoff celebration started at 8 O’Clock."</seg>
<seg id="13">It continued for two hours.</seg>
<seg id="14">The soldiers’ entertainment had completely finished.</seg>
<seg id="15">The youths started dispersing.</seg>
<seg id="16">We were going to leave as soon as it was finished.</seg>
<seg id="17">Just at that moment a gun was fired, it happened right in front of me.</seg>
<seg id="18">My granddaughter’s situation is not good.</seg>
<seg id="19">She has an 80–90% chance of losing her eye.</seg>
<seg id="20">We talked to the doctor and this is what he said.</seg>
<seg id="21">They extracted one of the buckshot while the other remained in her eye.</seg>
<seg id="22">"She has had surgery and might undergo ten operations.</seg>
<seg id="23">The suspects, M.K. and O.A., were captured and detained by the Eyüp District’s Security Directorate’s Public Security team.</seg>
<seg id="24">Two people were referred to the courthouse after the completion of the police investigation, and based on the evidence gathered, were arrested.</seg>
</p>
